  elapsedMs=300000
  configuredTimeoutMs=120000
  timeoutEventSeq=2
  inProgressArtifacts=[(none observable)]

Target-entry framing:
  You are transitioning from error into execution.
  The pathway recap above names the timeout evidence you are re-entering with.
  Continue with the normal execution flow; the full execution prompt will be emitted by \`gobbi workflow next\` on the next invocation."
`;

