InvalidTransition recap:
  rejectedEventType=workflow.step.exit
  rejectedEventSeq=null (rejected before append)
  stepAtRejection=plan
  reducerMessage=Cannot exit plan before plan_eval decision
  invalidTransitionEventSeq=2

Target-entry framing:
